description:
Adding this accountability factor to your health will get you the results you seek in all areas of life.
 
I had it backwards and thought I had to put business first before everything else. As a result, I got fat and out of shape.
 
In this episode, I’m going to show you how you can add accountability to get the results your after, and why this is so important for every area of your life.
